<BaseLayout title="How to Test a LoRA Safely" description="Test LoRA models with safe prompts, varied scenes, and original concepts." canonicalPath="/lora/testing-lora/"><article class="content-section article-body"><h1>How to Test a LoRA Safely</h1><p>Test a LoRA with simple prompts first, then vary camera angle, lighting, scene, and style. Use original concepts and avoid prompts that imitate real people or protected characters.</p><p>Build a small test grid and keep notes. If the LoRA only works in one exact prompt, the dataset or training settings may be too narrow.</p></article></BaseLayout>
